==English==

===Pronunciation===
*{{IPA|/ˌaɪsteðvɒd/}}
*/ā-stĕTH'vŏd/
*/eye-stĕTH'vŏd/

===Etymology===
[[Welsh]] ''eisteddfod'' (session), from ''[[eistedd]]'' (to sit) and ''[[bod]]'' (being).

===Noun===
{{en-noun-irreg|eisteddfods|eisteddfodau}}

# Any of several [[annual]] [[festival]]s in which [[Welsh]] [[poet]]s, [[dancer]]s and [[musician]]s [[compete]] for [[recognition]].

'''Eisteddfod motto'''

:"Byd gwyn fydd byd a gano,
:Gwaraidd fydd ei gerddi fo"

:''"Blessed is a world that sings,
:Gentle are its songs"''